description:
V4w.enko – “Earth5_cl7_CNVS03”.

Regression and progression as a black and white are forming the pattern – the pattern of “fast transformation”. The fast interpretation of the perception reacts on the most visible edges fast. The most reaction, the most analysis, the most transformation, the most result. Black and white pattern is the pattern of borders. When the rigids of black and white are fixed in mind then colors are started to possible to add. This canvas is formed from tiles of the animation arranged in time in one line from down left side to the top right corner. 3/9 proportion is applied to the canvas of the composition [.JPEG file, 6300*9300]
